{"sections":[{"estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"chapter":"Go further with more ressources","backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png","kind":"hero","title":"Going further with more resources","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you have learned how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and view modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"image":"ic_theme_intro.png"},{"kind":"tasks","tasks":[{"title":"More resources","stepsSection":[{"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can get it at ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}]}],"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc."}]}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png","code":null},{"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Go to the website and learn things at ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}]},{"text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","code":null},{"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Have a look ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki"},{"text":" to discover how OUDS works.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png","code":null},{"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For technical reasons the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"design system toolbox"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","code":null},{"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Do not hesitate to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"!","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS is open source, public and uses GitHub as forge. Thus, you will find common things inside the ","type":"text"},{"identif